		<title>POR.AUTOREPAIRPARTYENRICHMENT</title>
        <table>POR.AUTOREPAIRPARTYENRICHMENT</table>
    </header>
    <overview>
        <ovdesc>
        <p>The OLD values of fields that have been enriched.</p>
        </ovdesc>
    </overview>
    <menu>
	     <t>
            <field>ID</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Unique ID generated by the payments hub in order to identify each record in the application.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>CompanyID</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Indicates the company ID for which the record is created.</p>
                <p>Example: BNK,GB1</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>Mandatory field; 3 alphanumeric characters.</p>
                <p>The value links to the field 'CompanyID' in PPT.COMPANY.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>FTNumber</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Denotes the unique ID generated by the payments hub upon generating a payment order.</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>Mandatory field; 16 alphanumeric characters.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>			
        <t>
            <field>PartyRole</field>
            <desc>
                <p>For Debit Parties: Party Role Role Description Tag</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>6 numeric characters. </p>
                <p>Possible values:</p>				
				<p>  INSPTY Instructing Party 50 C or L</p>
				<p>  ORDPTY Ordering Party 50 A, F, G, H or K</p>
				<p>  SNDINS Sending Institution 51A</p>
				<p>  ASVINS Account Servicing Institution 52A or C</p>
				<p>  ORDINS Ordering Institution 52A or D</p>
				<p>  SNDCBK Sender's Correspondent Bank 53A, B or D</p>
				<p>  RCVCBK Receiver's Correspondent Bank 54A, B or D</p>
				<p>  TRMINS Third Reimbursement Institution 55A, B or D</p>
				<p>  SENDER Sender</p>
				<p>  IMPDBT Implied Debit Account</p>
				<p>  For Credit Parties:</p>
				<p>  BENFCY Beneficiary 59A or no letter option 50 C or L</p>
				<p>  IMPCDT Implied Credit 50 A, F, G, H or K</p>				
            </desc>
        </t>
